snippet: Iran and six world powers are set to resume low-level talks on Iran's nuclear program in Geneva on Jan 15, with wide gaps remaining in their positions, the Iranian foreign minister said....

headline.print_headline: Iran Says Nuclear Talks Set for Jan 15, Vows to Stand Firm
headline.main: Iran Says Nuclear Talks Set for Jan 15, Vows to Stand Firm

lead_paragraph: Iran and six world powers are set to resume low-level talks on Iran's nuclear program in Geneva on Jan 15, with wide gaps remaining in their positions, the Iranian foreign minister said.
